## Slide 18: Analysis of Competing Hypotheses (ACH)

**Thá»i lÆ°á»£ng:** 5-6 phÃºt

**Ká»‹ch báº£n:**

**ACH lÃ  gÃ¬?**

PhÆ°Æ¡ng phÃ¡p luáº­n Ä‘á»ƒ giáº£m bias trong phÃ¢n tÃ­ch, phÃ¡t triá»ƒn bá»Ÿi Richards Heuer Jr. (CIA, 45 nÄƒm kinh nghiá»‡m).

**Ã tÆ°á»Ÿng cá»‘t lÃµi:**

```
Thay vÃ¬: TÃ¬m evidence Ä‘á»ƒ CONFIRM Ä‘iá»u Ä‘Ã£ tin
         â†“
LÃ m:     ÄÃ¡nh giÃ¡ cÃ³ há»‡ thá»‘ng NHIá»€U hypotheses vá»›i Táº¤T Cáº¢ evidence
```

**Khi nÃ o dÃ¹ng ACH?**

| DÃ¹ng ACH khi... | KhÃ´ng cáº§n ACH khi... |
|-----------------|----------------------|
| High stakes decisions | Routine analysis |
| Multiple plausible explanations | Clear-cut cases |
| Significant uncertainty | Abundant evidence |
| Potential for bias | Low-impact assessments |

---

## Slide 19: ACH - Quy TrÃ¬nh 7 BÆ°á»›c

**Thá»i lÆ°á»£ng:** 6-8 phÃºt

