## Slide 23: Exercise 4.3 - ACH Matrix

**Thá»i lÆ°á»£ng:** 5-6 phÃºt

**Ká»‹ch báº£n:**

**Step 3: Map Evidence to Hypotheses**

| Evidence | H1 (Diversion) | H2 (Separate) | H3 (False +) | H4 (Insider) |
|----------|----------------|---------------|--------------|--------------|
| E1: Exfil trÆ°á»›c ransomware | + | - | - | - |
| E2: KhÃ´ng cÃ³ other intrusions | + | - | + | + |
| E3: TrickBot gáº§n temporal vá»›i exfil | + | - | - | - |
| E4: Outside firm confirm ransomware | 0 | 0 | - | 0 |
| E5: KhÃ´ng cÃ³ public diversion cases | - | + | 0 | 0 |
| E6: Robin Hood khÃ´ng overlap TrickBot | - | + | 0 | 0 |
| E7: Ryuk nhanh, delay táº¡o window | + | - | 0 | 0 |
| E8: Money Bin lÃ  financial org | 0 | 0 | 0 | 0 |

**Legend:** + = supports, - = refutes, 0 = neutral

**Step 4: Refinement**

